<h3 id="authentication-and-authorization">Authentication and Authorization</h3>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.sandersdenardi.com/aws-lambda-api-auth/">https://www.sandersdenardi.com/aws-lambda-api-auth/</a>
Create 3 separate api: login, logout, get with 3 Lambda functions, login will call to another authentication resource: YAML, Cognito, etc</li>
  <li><a href="https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/compute/introducing-custom-authorizers-in-amazon-api-gateway/">https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/compute/introducing-custom-authorizers-in-amazon-api-gateway/</a>
Custom Authorizer API Gateway</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/danilop/LambdAuth">https://github.com/danilop/LambdAuth</a> Lambda function for cognito</li>
  <li><a href="https://www.concurrencylabs.com/blog/configure-your-lambda-function-like-a-champ-sail-smoothly/">https://www.concurrencylabs.com/blog/configure-your-lambda-function-like-a-champ-sail-smoothly/</a>
Config lambda function with environment tag</li>
  <li><a href="https://gitlab.com/wingadium/ReadingDocument/blob/f21f586f2bae119d94c9c006c846783be31c9e26/Serverless%20Authentication%20AWS%20Re%20Invent%202016.pdf">AWS re:Invent Serverless Authentication and Authorization</a></li>
</ul>

